\f0\fs24 . It was one thing to arrive in an upscale carriage -like so many of the other guests- or to show up dressed in the finest silks money could buy. It was another thing entirely to arrive by airship. Even among the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://1731B8EC-617C-4081-B6E8-B0F64538D006"}}{\fldrslt ton}}, the 
