\f0\fs24 . \cb3 It was one thing to arrive in an upscale carriage -, like so many of the other guests-, or to show up dressed in the finest silks money could buy.\cb1  It was another thing entirely to arrive by airship. Even among the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://5BD88971-E74B-4626-A96A-2B444B0B3600"}}{\fldrslt ton}}, the 
