\f0\fs24 Finally, they had reached the entrance, and their turn came to enter the ball. The butler held out his hand for their invitations, but Mr. Grundy stepped aside.
\f1\fs20 \

\f0\fs24 \'93After you, Mr. Grimmer,\'94 he said.
\f1\fs20 \

