\f1\fs20 \

\f0\fs24 \'93Your invitation, sir?\'94 said the butler.
\f1\fs20 \

\f0\fs24 \'93I had it just a minute ago,\'94 Jonathan told him, bewildered. He was sure the invitation had been in his pocket. Anxiously, he checked his other pockets for the note from his father. He was relieved to find that it was still there.
