\f0\fs24  {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://32B30B3D-E55B-494C-B60D-AB0244CD4777"}}{\fldrslt He had one, a pistol, in his belt somewhere. He reached for it, drew the gun from his belt}}, but Connor\'92s killer was quicker. Much quicker.
\f1\fs20 \

\f0\fs24 \'93Drop it,\'94 said the killer, already on his feet. His voice was cold, threatening. He had already killed Connor. It seemed that, and Jonathan was now the only sole witness. It seemed unlikely that he would hesitate to shoot Jonathan now. He hesitated to relinquish his weapon, but it {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://00DDDBD0-003E-427E-938D-6BA1E88221FE"}}{\fldrslt seemed}} he had little choice but to do as the killer asked. Taking care not to make any sudden moves, he set the gun on the floor.
\f1\fs20 \

\f0\fs24 \'93Kick it over here.\'94
\f1\fs20 \
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://FFAED2A8-D9DB-4111-B7E0-757FD99DD4E9"}}{\fldrslt 
\f0\fs24 Jonathan did as directed.}}\
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://D09BD949-10F7-49E6-8B7E-D575A08D442F"}}{\fldrslt 
\f0\fs24 When he stood, the killer had moved closer and had his pistol aimed directly at Jonathan\'92s face. His own weapon had been stuffed into the killer\'92s belt.}}\

\f0\fs24 \'93What are you doing here?\'94 the killer asked him. Jonathan noticed that though his tone was threatening, his voice was high in pitch, almost feminine.
\f1\fs20 \

\f0\fs24 \'93I heard gunfire,\'94 Jonathan told him, just barely managing to keep his voice even. He would have killed for a {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://C98BB909-E7C9-423F-BB85-04D9EC63EC0C"}}{\fldrslt glass of absinthe }}right now. Anything to steady his nerves.
\f1\fs20 \
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://C30C89C1-37F3-4BD7-B568-15630A5EB0C0"}}{\fldrslt 
\f0\fs24 The killer cursed. \'93I\'92d hoped the applause would drown it out,\'94 he said}}
