\f0\fs24 \cf0 Annabel stooped down to get another look at Lord Connor. She needed to roll him onto his back to do so, and he was heavy. Damn heavy. She huffed with the effort as she heaved him onto his back. His head rolled, giving her a clear view of the exit wound at the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivcmt://554A8281-6E83-4E69-8CB9-916154377163"}}{\fldrslt back o}}f his skull.
\f1\fs20 \
